>> source: Forks Over Knives
>> serves: 6

Boil @Yukon gold potatoes{1%lb} in a #steamer basket{} until tender, 10 to ~{15%minutes}.

Transfer to a #food processor{} with @unsweetened almond milk{1%cup}, @nutritional yeast{6%Tbsps}, @lemon juice{1%Tbsp}, @garlic{2%cloves}, @cayenne{1%pinch}.

Puree until smooth.
